<plot>Kumeyaay, are one of the many Native American tribes split by the USA-Mexican border. In Baja California a Kumeyaay elder, master basket weaver, mobilizes her village to turn ancient traditions into modern commodities. She walks the delicate line between product and sacred tradition as she finds survival in the weave.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?523418</url></doc>
